            <div class="copy">
                <p class="meta">2018-02-09 France</p>
                <h3 class="title">
                    <a title="Saving France&#039;s city centres: How to lure back locals?" href="/en/20180209-france-focus-urban-desertification-city-centres-mayors-shops-residents-dreux" class="modeless">
                        Saving France's city centres: How to lure back locals?
                    </a>
                </h3>
                <p class="desc">
                   This week, we're in the northern French city of Dreux, famed for its rich history, royal chapel and... boarded-up shops. Like a number of cities in France, Dreux has fallen prey...
                </p>
            </div>

                                        
